## Live API spot-check (proxy against group-pas-dev)

`GET /api/quotation/quotes/170ea9b1.../memberToPlanMappingJson` parsed shape:

```json
{
  "decisionTable": {
    "hitPolicy": "FIRST",
    "inputs":  [{"id":"salary",   "label":"Annual Salary", "typeRef":"number"}],
    "outputs": [{"id":"planNo",   "label":"Plan",          "typeRef":"string"}],
    "rules": [
      {"when": {"salary": ">= 2000000"}, "then": {"planNo": "P2"}},
      {"when": {"salary": "< 2000000"},  "then": {"planNo": "P1"}}
    ]
  }
}
```

The proposal assumed `hits` and `rules` at the top level; the real shape nests them under `decisionTable` and uses `when` / `then` per rule (not `if` / `then`). Column set is dynamic ŌĆö N inputs + M outputs.

